<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>The Monsters Ring</span>, <span>The Skull Of Truth</span>, <span>Juliet Dove Queen Of Love</span>, <span>Jennifer Murdleys Toad</span>, <span>Jeremy Thatcher Dragon Hatcher</span>, <span>The Metamorphosis Of Justin Jones</span> </h3>
